upload-with-content-type.display-name: Upload a file with a content type

__package__.yml.rawContents:
service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    upload-file:
      path: /upload
      method: POST
      auth: false
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      display-name: Upload a file
      request:
        name: UploadFileRequest
        body:
          properties:
            file:
              type: file
              docs: The file to upload
            maybe_file:
              type: optional<file>
              docs: An optional file to upload
        content-type: multipart/form-data
      examples:
        - request: {}
    upload-list:
      path: /upload-list
      method: POST
      auth: false
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      display-name: Upload a list of files
      request:
        name: UploadListRequest
        body:
          properties:
            list_file: list<file>
            maybe_list_file: optional<list<file>>
        content-type: multipart/form-data
      examples:
        - request: {}
    upload-with-content-type:
      path: /upload-with-content-type
      method: POST
      auth: false
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      display-name: Upload a file with a content type
      request:
        name: UploadWithContentTypeRequest
        body:
          properties:
            file:
              type: file
              docs: The file to upload
              content-type: application/octet-stream
            maybe_file:
              type: optional<file>
              docs: An optional file to upload
            metadata:
              type: optional<map<string, unknown>>
              docs: This is a metadata field
              content-type: application/json
            data:
              type: optional<UploadWithContentTypeRequestData>
              style: exploded
        content-type: multipart/form-data
      examples:
        - request: {}
  source:
    openapi: ../openapi.yml
types:
  UploadWithContentTypeRequestData:
    properties:
      datum: optional<string>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
    inline: true

rootApiFile.rawContents:
name: api
error-discrimination:
  strategy: status-code
display-name: Test file upload
